П.А. Гладких
P.A. Gladkikh is associated with the Perm National Research Polytechnic University and is involved in research related to Taylor-Bishop-Hill models.

Пермский национальный исследовательский политехнический университет
Perm National Research Polytechnic University is an educational institution located in Perm, Russian Federation.

г. Пермь
Perm is a city in the Russian Federation.

Тейлора – Бишопа – Хилла
Taylor-Bishop-Hill models are a type of constitutive model used in material science to address uncertainties in active system selection and shear rate calculations.

Конститутивные модели (КМ)
Конститутивные модели (КМ) are mathematical models used to describe the physical mechanisms of irreversible changes in material structures.

Физические теории пластичности (ФТП)
Физические теории пластичности (ФТП) include various models such as rigid-plastic, elastic-plastic, viscoelastic, viscoplastic, and elastoviscoplastic models.
